name: 5ivecanons
description: We’re a team of opinionated and dedicated creatives, passionate about our work and our process. Some of us are console and some are PC, but at the end of the day it’s the passion for our work that drives us to be better than the day before. And even though we may not agree on whether the original 1989 Batman movie was better than Dark Knight or not, we can agree that it’s… a movie.
